{
  "stem": "22174.7",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And-- and blamed by these-- by these mostly middle class right wing people but not-- but not by the working people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And those working people were-- 95% of our customers were working people and-- and socialists.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the-- I have to come back to things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- on the first of April, 1933-- what was that, two months after the Nazi take over?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was declared a day of boycott of all Jewish establishments and stores.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So in the morning, two Nazis-- wore brown shirts-- positioned themselves in the-- at the entrance to our store to prevent people from going in and-- and-- and buying something.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But all the day long, people, our customers, came in and asked my parents just to make them up a-- a-- a package.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- not to put nothing in there, just make them package, as if they had bought something, just a show of defiance to those Nazis.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then in the evening, at 6 o'clock, when the last shift of Nazis left, one of our non-Jewish saleswomen took a pail of water and a scrubber, and she scrubbed those two spots where these-- these two Nazis had stood, like mad.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You  know, like the scrubbing of dirt in-- in front of anybody in the street that wanted to look at it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] there were these kind of people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were-- they-- and as I said, there was a really strong movement of pacifism in Germany.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- I was very much influenced by that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and also, [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] personality-wise, I always was against-- against injustices.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even today, I can't take-- I can't-- I can't-- I have a hard time to cope with injustice and-- and violence.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
